# StudyFlow â€“ Smart Study Planner

StudyFlow is a responsive web-based study planner that helps students manage subjects, tasks, study sessions, and track progress in one organised dashboard.

## Features

- Dashboard overview (subjects, tasks, study hours)
- Subject management with priority and custom colours
- Task tracking with deadlines and filters (pending, completed, overdue)
- Study session scheduling with time slots
- Progress analytics and weekly stats
- Theme toggle and local data storage
- Data export and reset options

## Tech Stack

- HTML5
- CSS3
- Vanilla JavaScript
- Browser Local Storage

## Project Structure

- index.html
- styles.css
- script.js
- readme

## How to Run

1. Open index.html in your browser
2. No backend or server required

## Future Scope

- Backend integration
- Authentication system
- Cloud sync
- AI-based study insights